These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, techno, jazz
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | techno | hip-hop | d&b | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, cat, rat, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | horse | rat | cat | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, dancing, chess
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | dancing | fishing | card-games | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | bus | quad-bike | airplane | taxi |

