1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | crime | comedy | mystery |

